Adding Visual Charts- GPM By State Line and Clustered Column Chart 22

Visual 2 'GPM By State'




1. Copy and paste the GPM By Month chart and resize the visual to fit the space.
2. Fill in the figures provided below for the necessary fields.
Click on an empty space on the canvas, from the Visualization pane Select Line and Clustered Column Char
Fill the value fields provided below for the necessary fields
Build Visual:
X-Axis = State
Column Y-Axis = Active Cust , Churned Cust
Line Y-Axis = GPM
Tooltips = GPM, Active Cust, Churned Cust, State
Format Visual:
General:

Width = 364
Horizontal = 575
Vertical = 62

Text = GPM By State
Font = Segoe UI, Size = 12
Text color = # FFFFFF
Background color = # 094780
Horizontal Alignment = Center
Background -> On
Color = #F1F7F6
Transparency = 0%
Header Icons -> on
Color-> Background = #FFFFFF, Border = #FFFFFF, Icon = #000000
Transparency = 0%
Tooltip -> On
Text: Font = Segoe UI, Size = 9, Label Color = #252423, Value color = #252423
Background -> Color = #FFFFFF, Transparency = 0%
Visual:
X-Axis =>Values=on: Font = Segoe UI, Size = 9, Color =#000000, Title = off
Y-Axis ->value= On, Font = Segoe UI, Size = 12, Color =#000000, Title = off
Secondary Y-Axis => On, Values: Font = Segoe UI, Size = 12, Color =#000000, Title = off
